author: kfogel
msg: (close_file): print out 'G' for merges.
This will work when Ben checks in his pending timestamp sophistication
fixes.  For now, 'U' is printed whether the update caused a merge or
not, because my original code wrongly sets the timestamp even on
merge, thus fooling svn_wc_file_modified_p().
